      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's what i keep telling myself. \"just a different perspective,\" \"just keep trying.\" it's just words. it doesn't change the fact that the loop just keeps spinning. it feels like i'm just a glitch in a system that's designed to fail. there's no actual way out of the pattern.",
